'''Renhuai''' ({{zh|s=仁怀 |t=仁懷 |p=Rénhuái}}) is a [[county-level city]] located in the north of [[Guizhou]] province, China, bordering [[Sichuan]] province to the west. It is under the administration of the [[prefecture-level city]] of [[Zunyi]].
==Administrative divisions== * Under the jurisdiction of Renhuai, it is subdivided into 19 township-level divisions (13 towns and 6 townships); subdivided into 22 communities and 149 villages.
